    {
      "id": "BTjyBaU6HjBtRZQhW_Mr9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1373.9285714285713,
      "y": 202.38094983782088,
      "width": 573.19970703125,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1L",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1621504066,
      "version": 302,
      "versionNonce": 2093609147,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781999955396,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The AI team will ask themselves multiple questions:-\n\n    - To academic department:-\n        . How many student take admission in previous year?\n        .  how many student take admission in current year?\n        ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The AI team will ask themselves multiple questions:-\n\n    - To academic department:-\n        . How many student take admission in previous year?\n        .  how many student take admission in current year?\n        ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "XJkfhpfHB5Soot4U6XFBl",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1397.0952453613281,
      "y": 357.69047982352123,
      "width": 790.759521484375,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1N",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1601922334,
      "version": 553,
      "versionNonce": 229130926,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782093117024,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- To hostel administration cell :-\n    . how many student take hostel rooms in previous year?\n    . which rooms is more preferred by students?\n    . how many student take hostel rooms in current year?\n    . what is fee structure for different rooms(single, double, triple sharing room)\n      in previous year with and without AC?\n    . what is fee structure for different rooms(single, double, triple sharing room)\n      in current year with and without AC?\n    . any changes take in fee structure in current year?",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- To hostel administration cell :-\n    . how many student take hostel rooms in previous year?\n    . which rooms is more preferred by students?\n    . how many student take hostel rooms in current year?\n    . what is fee structure for different rooms(single, double, triple sharing room)\n      in previous year with and without AC?\n    . what is fee structure for different rooms(single, double, triple sharing room)\n      in current year with and without AC?\n    . any changes take in fee structure in current year?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "j9T6EBJqSL3DQkV7UfV_C",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1411.6137593587239,
