      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782087555035,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- To Hostel warden :-\n    . what is the hostel entry timing?\n    . what is the hostel exit timing?\n    . what is the curfew timing? ",
