      "text": "Suppose the administration cell reverts the following answer\n    . 3000 student take admission in previous year\n    . 4000 student take admission in current year\n    . 300 student take hostel rooms in previous year\n    . double sharing room is more prefered by student\n    . 400 student take hostel rooms in current year\n    .  This is the fee structure for previous year :-",
