      "updated": 1782088368235,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Step 2:-   Define the problem precisely\n\n- Poor problem statement\n    ~ \"hostel room prediction system\"\n\n- Better approach\n    ~ \" identify how many student take hostel in next year\n        on the basis of admission and rules and fee structure\n        so that administration cell can give more facility to it and\n         prevent room shortage\". ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Step 2:-   Define the problem precisely\n\n- Poor problem statement\n    ~ \"hostel room prediction system\"\n\n- Better approach\n    ~ \" identify how many student take hostel in next year\n        on the basis of admission and rules and fee structure\n        so that administration cell can give more facility to it and\n         prevent room shortage\". ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
