      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": " Step 5 :- Define the AI tasks\n\n    - Machine learning formulation:-\n        - classification problem\n            - output -> take hostel room= yes/ take hostel room= no\n                - binary classification problem\n    \n    - Risk scoring\n        -How likely take hostel room? 0-100%\n\n    - ranking problem :-\n        - top 200 student whose take hostel room\n           give 10% discount",
