      "text": "step 7 :- Defining constraints\n\n    . operational constraints:-\n        - administration cell can only give 10% discount to top 200 student \n\n    . Time constraints :-\n        - before starting the next admission session\n\n    . Data constraints :-\n        - certain information is not exist :-\n            - mental health indicators\n            - family circumstances\n            - updated financial records\n    \n    . ethical constraints :-\n        - students should not be harmed\n\n            - not share student personal data\n            - no discriminayion\n          \n",
